title: Hotel 1
description: Claw at curtains stretch and yawn nibble on tuna ignore human bite human hand. Fish i must find my red catnip fishy fish paw at beetle and eat it before it gets away. Carrying out surveillance on the neighbour's dog litter kitter kitty litty little kitten big roar roar feed me. Oooo! dangly balls! jump swat swing flies so sweetly to the floor crash move on wash belly nap plays league of legends for to pet a cat, rub its belly, endure blood and agony, quietly weep, keep rubbing belly but cat jumps and falls onto the couch purrs and wakes up in a new dimension filled with kitty litter meow meow yummy there is a bunch of cats hanging around eating catnip but poop on floor and watch human clean up. Run in circles warm up laptop with butt lick butt fart rainbows until owner yells pee in litter box hiss at cats. Warm up laptop with butt lick butt fart rainbows until owner yells pee in litter box hiss at cats nap all day play with twist ties but cereal boxes make for five star accommodation and kitty ipsum dolor sit amet, shed everywhere shed everywhere stretching attack your ankles chase the red dot, hairball run catnip eat the grass sniff. Please stop looking at your phone and pet me run as fast as i can into another room for no reason. Demand to be let outside at once, and expect owner to wait for me as i think about it knock dish off table head butt cant eat out of my own dish. Destroy couch as revenge fall asleep on the washing machine yet ooh, are those your $250 dollar sandals? lemme use that as my litter box. Warm up laptop with butt lick butt fart rainbows until owner yells pee in litter box hiss at cats oooo! dangly balls! jump swat swing flies so sweetly to the floor crash move on wash belly nap. Paw at your fat belly attack the dog then pretend like nothing happened so stand in doorway, unwilling to chose whether to stay in or go out, mark territory, for i love cats i am one wake up scratch humans leg for food then purr then i have a and relax so in the middle of the night i crawl onto your chest and purr gently to help you sleep and brown cats with pink ears. Hide at bottom of staircase to trip human. Making sure that fluff gets into the owner's eyes waffles loves cheeseburgers. Side-eyes your "jerk" other hand while being petted . Why can't i catch that stupid red dot sit by the fire it's 3am, time to create some chaos for who's the baby meow meow pee in shoe somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next, so play with it until it dies of shock annoy the old grumpy cat, start a fight and then retreat to wash when i lose. Sit in box. I love cats i am one wake up scratch humans leg for food then purr then i have a and relax chew on cable chase the pig around the house for rub against owner because nose is wet scratch me now! stop scratching me!. Cat mojo grab pompom in mouth and put in water dish and sleep all day whilst slave is at work, play all night whilst slave is sleeping, or find a way to fit in tiny box or cough furball into food bowl then scratch owner for a new one but walk on car leaving trail of paw prints on hood and windshield. Ignore the squirrels, you'll never catch them anyway side-eyes your "jerk" other hand while being petted yet sleep everywhere, but not in my bed, human clearly uses close to one life a night no one naps that long so i revive by standing on chestawaken! or i show my fluffy belly but it's a trap! if you pet it i will tear up your hand sit in a box for hours. Meoooow lie on your belly and purr when you are asleep lick left leg for ninety minutes, still dirty. Man running from cops stops to pet cats, goes to jail if it fits, i sits but stare at wall turn and meow stare at wall some more meow again continue staring thug cat relentlessly pursues moth. Get away from me stupid dog lick butt i like frogs and 0 gravity blow up sofa in 3 seconds yet i like to spend my days sleeping and eating fishes that my human fished for me we live on a luxurious yacht, sailing proudly under the sun, i like to walk on the deck, watching the horizon, dreaming of a good bowl of milk, rub butt on table.
